modName: The lord and mighty Talos statues of windhelm
summary: Adds two massive Statues of Talos on each side of Windhelm its a beautiful sight to see in skyrim
descriptionHtml:
The mod adds two massive statues of Talos on each side of Windhelm this beautiful sight to see in skyrim if you want Windhelm to look diffrent in your skyrim  give it a look and a try the statues are massive.  


In this mod you dont get the green mossy look that\'s seen in the images that\'s just from another mod  that is built into my game you wont have that unless you have some texture mods installed i have the mossy rock textures mod on my copy of skyrim so it shows up with moss on the statues it wont be there on yours okay :D awesome enjoy. Also am only running skyrim on medium setttings till I upgrade my Gpu so if you have a good pc it will look far more interesting on your own machine then it does from the screenshots i have taken  :) 

HOW to install :D ! 
1.1 file update added a new statue to winter hold unistall version 1.0 in skyrim nexus if you have that installed and just have 1.1 installed instead and your good to go if your new to the mod just install 1.1 and you are good to go :D okay awesome enjoy :D
author: Dinoworld112
